{"id":1,"name":"新角色名"}

### 3.5 删除角色（admin 直通）
POST {{ADMIN}}/v1/auth/role/deleteByIds
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

{"ids":[999]}


